{"h4c51333eg819fg4c62g9a02gc5353ce4722a": ["*The eye doesn't seem to notice your presence.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "386aef3f-ea39-0d2f-332c-42ca47186d53"], "h96c3516cg98ebg4aa3ga3a4g415f833c7eb5": ["*The eye's glassy black surface reflects your gaze.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "6495646d-4dc4-0861-90e2-2fccfbbcbc05"], "h7672fd15g5f74g4fe9g9397g0ba8a17721dd": ["*As you gaze deeper, you feel a focus. An <i>intent</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "dd7facfb-3f8b-55f4-e58a-e9aefaae6882"], "h6812320bg5927g4e67g8c0bgaafef0e15f75": ["<i>Reach out to the presence.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "8f1124ba-9009-cb02-6cca-5b256dacc71b"], "h61076e02g040eg482egb9dfgf34bc95ff435": ["*You feel a brief, lurching connection. The sensation of falling into your own image, endlessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "d34e6354-fce0-f318-8abe-d6aa94dbb7ce"], "h04dcd239g3a74g46c5g8513gb9503027bf80": ["*Confusion. Alarm. Then the presence withdraws - leaving a dull black mirror once more.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "5cd2e703-0e7a-0c6d-16b8-2819bf304cd9"], "hb1bef656ga1f1g4051g901eg38e7c0d555df": ["<i>Poke it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "e258d126-5be6-7040-d963-6921032596fd"], "hbc251191gb2d9g4e6dg8a87gace725c6e6b1": ["*You sense no reaction from the unblinking eye.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "9a77efee-9733-e566-0d0f-1a38131ae1a4"], "hcca07eb2g9538g494cg8640g06b09f5db37a": ["<i>Glare back at it.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "9d111aba-9c4f-c4ff-41e2-c8b68505bab3"], "h17697747g8a15g4accgbff6g539cfcf39d04": ["<i>Give a cheerful wave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "9d111aba-9c4f-c4ff-41e2-c8b68505bab3"], "hefd1e5ebg8de8g47f5g9acagfce34dd2b5a5": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Eye.html", "51d5014d-c94d-b454-9da7-cb64371f058f"]}